{
  "headers": [
    {
      "source": "/Build/(.*)",
      "headers": [
        { "key": "Content-Encoding", "value": "br" }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

This is stripped down to the absolute minimum — just one rule, no Content-Type overrides, applied to everything in `/Build/`. Vercel is stricter about `vercel.json` schema than most expect, and extra fields can cause silent rejections.

